<h1>Welcome to the License Key Generator!</h1>

<p>This web application allows you to generate unique license keys for your software products and validate them.</p>

<p>To get started, please navigate to the "Generate Key" page and fill out the required information, including your full name, the name of your software product, and the authentication secret. Then, click the "Generate Key" button to receive your unique license key.</p>

<p>To validate a license key, navigate to the "Validate License Key" page and enter your full name and the license key you wish to validate. Then, click the "Validate" button to see if the license key is valid.</p>

<p>Thank you for using the License Key Generator. If you have any questions or concerns, please contact our support team.</p>
